reviewText:
George and Barbara Bush give a tour thru the living quarters of the White House.  You are taken thru some of the most beautiful private rooms on the 2nd floor , and some really great personal one on one conversation included with George and Barbara Bush concerning issues of the day.  The family and grandchildren are included, on a visit to Kennebunkport the

family compound.  Very enjoyable.  And Millie is starring too!  Who could resist that?!
